我岩岩再睇番段新聞其實唔算串我哋<img src="/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif" class="hkgmoji" />， 不過嗰時咁岩輸左三球俾維拉， 就有依段訪問出黎， 我自己有啲自卑心態先咁覺得<img src="/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif" class="hkgmoji" />。其實佢咁講算正路， 去維拉始終俾留隊阿仙奴多好多機會打正選， 對佢嚟講一定係好事。<br />
<br />
&ldquo;Aston Villa is a massive club, I had no doubts over coming here. Everyone thinks it's a step down going from Arsenal to Villa, but I actually think it's a step up in my career.&rdquo;
